UNCOMPLICATED FIRE WALL :

    CHECK STATUS : ufw status

    ENABLE FIREWALL : ufw enable

    DISABLE FIREWALL : ufw disable

    ALLOW ALL OUTGOING CONNECTIONS : sudo ufw default allow outgoing

    DENY INCOMING TRAFFIC AT A PORT : sudo ufw deny Port_Num/Protocol_Name

    LIST ACTIVE RULES IN ORDER : sudo ufw status numbered

    DELETE A RULE : sudo ufw delete Rule_Number
    